                        <span class="text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] font-titillium font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Monterrey, N.L.</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="font-titillium text-[#343233] text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-5 sm:mb-5 sm:mb-6 flex-grow">Proyecto integral de acometida, media tensión y distribución de fuerza para sistemas HVAC en nueva sucursal.</p>
                    <div class="flex justify-start mt-auto">
                        <a href="#" class="group/btn flex items-stretch gap-[2px] h-9 sm:h-9 sm:h-10">
                            <div class="bg-[#B21508] text-white text-[10px] sm:text-[11px] font-titillium font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 sm:px-4 sm:px-6 flex items-center group-hover/btn:bg-[#8f1106] transition duration-300 rounded-l-md">Ver Detalles</div>
